{CHARACTER_NAME}: CYPHER
{DIALOGUE}: He's going to pop!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vomiting violently, Neo pitches forward and blacks out.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. NEO'S ROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He blinks, regaining consciousness.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The room is dark.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo is stretched out on his bed.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: I can't go back, can I?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus sitting like a shadow on a chair in the far corner.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
{DIALOGUE}: No.
{DIALOGUE}: But if you could, would you really want to?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo isn't sure of that answer.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
{DIALOGUE}: I feel that I owe you an apology.
{DIALOGUE}: There is a rule that we do not free a mind once it reaches a certain age.
{DIALOGUE}: It is dangerous.
{DIALOGUE}: They have trouble letting go.
{DIALOGUE}: Their mind turns against them.
{DIALOGUE}: I've seen it happen.
{DIALOGUE}: I broke the rule because I had to.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He stares into the darkness, confessing as much to himself as Neo.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
{DIALOGUE}: When the Matrix was first built there was a man born inside that had the ability to change what he wanted, to remake the Matrix as he saw fit.
{DIALOGUE}: It was this man that freed the first of us and taught us the secret of the war; control the Matrix and you control the future.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He pauses.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
{DIALOGUE}: When he died, the Oracle at the temple of Zion prophesied his return and envisioned an end to the war and freedom for our people.
{DIALOGUE}: That is why there are those of us that have spent our entire lives searching the Matrix, looking for him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo can feel his eyes on him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
{DIALOGUE}: I did what I did, because I believe we have been brought here for a reason, Neo.
{DIALOGUE}: You are here to serve a purpose, just as I am here to serve mine.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: I told you I don't believe in fate.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus smiles, leaning towards hin.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
{DIALOGUE}: But I do, Neo.
{DIALOGUE}: I do.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He stands up.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
