{DIALOGUE}: You're going to need it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: For what?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MORPHEUS
{DIALOGUE}: Your training.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HOVERCRAFT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There is no morning; there is only darkness and then the fluorescent light sticks flicker on.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. NEO'S ROOM
