{DIALOGUE}: Like an actor.
{DIALOGUE}: You can do that, right?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: AGENT SMITH
{DIALOGUE}: Whatever you want, Mr. Reagan.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cypher takes a deep drink of wine.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CYPHER
{DIALOGUE}: All right.
