{DIALOGUE}: It would be the end of us.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He looks up at Trinity who is pacing relentlessly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TANK
{DIALOGUE}: We can't let that happen.
{DIALOGUE}: We have to do it, Trinity.
{DIALOGUE}: Zion has to be protected.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Trinity sees Cypher's dead body.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Rage overtakes her and she starts kicking hin.
