{DIALOGUE}: Goddamnit!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TANK
{DIALOGUE}: We have to pull the plug.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TRINITY
{DIALOGUE}: No!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TANK
{DIALOGUE}: We don't have any other choice.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Those words are like using gasoline to put out a fire and we watch the pain in her eyes burn into a blaze.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She walks past him and gets into her chair.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TANK
{DIALOGUE}: Trinity, what are you doing?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TRINITY
{DIALOGUE}: I'm going in after him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TANK
{DIALOGUE}: Morpheus could conform at any minute --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TRINITY
