{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. ELEVATOR SHAFT (MATRIX) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hanging by a rope, Trinity hot-wires the panel for the door.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. TOP FLOOR (MATRIX) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nervous, the Marines watch as the ELEVATOR "DINGS" softly and slides open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Black smoke rises out of the exposed shaft.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The nearest Marine eases to the edge, peering down at the churning blaze engulfing the lower levels.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He does not see Trinity and Neo above him until it is too late.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Krack!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo kicks, knocking the Marine flying down into the shaft.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Before the others can react, Trinity flips out into the hall, decking the nearest Marine.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo cracks another.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The fight is over before it begins.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. PRESIDENTIAL SUITE (MATRIX) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An enormous EXPLOSION THUNDERS above them, shaking the building.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ALARM SOUNDS, emergency sprinklers begin showering the room.
