{CHARACTER_NAME}: AGENT SMITH
{DIALOGUE}: Find them and destroy them!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Jones nods and touches his ear piece.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. ROOF (MATRIX) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The roof-access tower is now engulfed in flames as Neo and Trinity lay waste to a dozen more Marines.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Guns and knives, like extensions of their bodies used with the same deadly precision as their feet and their fists.
