{CHARACTER_NAME}: PILOT
{DIALOGUE}: I repeat, we are under attack!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Suddenly his face, his whole body dissolves, consumed by spreading locust-like swarm, of STATIC as --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Jones emerges.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Just as she drops the last Marine, Trinity sees what's coming.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo sees her, the fear in her face, and he knows what is behind him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Screaming, he whirls, GUNS filling his hands with thought-speed.
