{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Agent blurred with motion --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Until the HAMMERS CLICK against empty metal.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: Trinity!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Jones charges.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: ... help.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His GUN BOOMS as we enter the liquid space of --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bullet-time.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The AIR SIZZLES with wads of lead-like angry flies as Neo twists, bends, ducks just between them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Jones still running, narrows the gap, the BULLETS coming faster until --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo bent impossibly back, one hand on the ground as a spiraling gray ball shears open his shoulder.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He starts to scream as another digs a red groove across his thigh.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He has only time to look up, to see the barrel when Agent Jones, standing over him, pulls the TRIGGER the final time.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLICK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Empty.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo rolls, reaching for another gun when around-house kick snaps his jaw.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Jones grabs the gun and levels it at Neo.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: AGENT JONES
{DIALOGUE}: Only human...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Suddenly Agent Jones stops.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Something is wrong.
