{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. PRESIDENTIAL SUITE (MATRIX) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Jones throws open the bedroom door and enters, walking through the puddles pooling in the carpet.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Over the RUSHING WATER and the ALARMS, Agent Smith hears a SOUND and understands the seriousness of the attack.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He turns to the wall of windows as the helicopter drops INTO VIEW --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo is in the back bay, aiming the mounted .50 machine gun.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: AGENT SMITH
{DIALOGUE}: No.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The GUN jumps and BULLETS EXPLODE through the WINDOW in a cacophony of CRASHING GLASS --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As the Agents go for their weapons.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: But Neo is too close, the .50 CALIBER too fast and BULLETS are everywhere, perforating the room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Smith is hit first, his body jack-knifing back, blood arcing out with a sudden flash of light --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then Agent Brown, his GUN still FIRING as his body falls.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And finally Agent Jones.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo stares at Morpheus, trying to will him into action.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: Get up, Morpheus!
{DIALOGUE}: Get up!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus sits unmoving, his head still down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo grabs the climbing rope just as marines burst into the adjoining room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He attaches only one end to his harness when they OPEN FIRE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Quickly he swings the GUN, SPRAYING the other room, WINDOWS SHATTERING, FURNITURE EXPLODING, marines diving for cover.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HALL (MATRIX) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Just outside the Presidential Suite, three marines blister with snow-static.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. PRESIDENTIAL SUITE (MATRIX) - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus lifts his face into the room's rain.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His eyes, still white, begin to blink, twitch, then close.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And when he opens them, they are again dark and flashing with fire.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Agents knife into the room, FIRING even as Neo's BULLET TRAILS chase them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus strains at his handcuffs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Agents and the marines turn the tide, BLASTING LEAD, RICOCHETING, POCK-MARKING the COPTER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FIRING wildly, Neo turns to see Morpheus rising, snapping the handcuffs, starting for the window.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Agent Smith stops and sees Morpheus run past the open bedroom door.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: AGENT SMITH
{DIALOGUE}: Nooo!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He FIRES, sweeping across the sheetrocked wall in a perfect line.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: For an instant, we see the BULLETS SHRED, PUNCTURING the WALL, searing through the wet air with jet trails of chalk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And as Morpheus starts to dive for the window, a bullet buries itself in his leg --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Knocking him off balance.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: He won't make it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus lunges, out of control --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As Neo spins, every move a whip crack --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Snapping the other rope-end onto a bolted bar.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus begins to fall when Neo hurls himself into the wide blue empty space --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Flying for a moment.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The rope snaking out behind him; an umbilical cord attached to a machine.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As their two bodies, set in motion, rushing at each other on a seemingly magnetic course until --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They collide.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Almost bouncing free of each other, arms, legs, scrambling, hands searching in furious desperation, finding hold and clinging.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Until the line ends, snapping taut, cracking their fragile embrace.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus tumbles, legs flipping over, falling down --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ground deliriously distant --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As Neo snatches hold of his mentor's still handcuffed wrist.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: Gotcha!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Trinity is already pulling the copter up and away.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As Agent Smith grabs the M-16 from the nearest marine.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He'll bring them all down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Targeting the helicopter, he aims at something only he can see: the oil line.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PONK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PONK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PONK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The rear HULL is PUNCHED full of holes and smoke and oil pours out like black blood.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TRINITY
{DIALOGUE}: Shit-shit-no!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo is pulling Morpheus up to him when he hears the HELICOPTER BEGIN TO DIE.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEO
{DIALOGUE}: Oh fuck.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Trinity throws the helicopter towards the roof of the nearest building.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Morpheus and Neo cling to one another as they and the machine above them begin to fall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ENGINE GRINDS, the CHOPPING BLADES start to slow while --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Agents stand in the open shattered window, watching the helicopter disappear behind taller buildings.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Carried by its nomentum, Trinity guides the parabolic fall over the nearest roof where --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo and Morpheus drop safely, rolling free as the rope goes slack.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo gets to his feet, trying to detach himself but --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The helicopter is falling too fast, arcing over the roof like a setting sun --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The coils of slack snap taught --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Yanking Neo off his feet, dragging him with ferocious speed towards the edge even as --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Trinity lunges for the back door, her gun in one hand, grabbing for the rope with the other --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Neo flies like a skipping stone, hurtling straight AT us, when his feet hit the rain gutter --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A fulcrum that levers him up just as --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Trinity FIRES, severing the cord from the HELICOPTER, falling free of it as it SMASHES, blades first into a glass skyscraper.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Holding onto the rope she swings, connected to Neo, who stands on the building's edge watching her arc beneath him as the HELICOPTER EXPLODES --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She bounces against a shatterproof window that spider- cracks out while FLAMES ERUPT behind her.
